text: Röhrmoos station is a railway station in the municipality of Röhrmoos, located in the Dachau district in Upper Bavaria, Germany. ==References== ==External links== Category:Munich S-Bahn stations Category:Railway stations in Bavaria Category:Railway stations in Germany opened in 1867 Category:1867 establishments in Bavaria Category:Buildings and structures in Dachau (district)
